-add sounds on the state transition of a model using a directories "start",
"end" and "running" from which sounds are randomly chosen. the "running" sound
should be played in a loop, the other sounds just once
-add a directory media/music where custom music is placed
-add a game variable which measures the "calmness" or "actionness" of the
current game on a discrete scale. the use can specify his own music files and
attach an action number to it so the music is played only when the game is at a
specific state
